â€œI need an onboarding form for new employees with fields for name, department, joining date, and manager.â€
	2.	Claude Request:
	â€¢	Prompt is sent to Claude via backend API.
	â€¢	Claude returns a structured form schema (JSON) with fields, types, validation rules, and UI hints.
