	â€¢	On form submit, data is validated.
	â€¢	Optional: AI validates business logic or offers refinement (â€œDo you want to add a signature field?â€)
	â€¢	Form can be iteratively improved using new prompts, enabling agentic flow (Claude as a form-design assistant).

